    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. While it remains mechanically sound enough for regular use, it does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches, minor dings, and slight paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and tear, and while the major components like the engine and transmission are operational, you should expect the typical quirks associated with a well-used vehicle. It is a solid choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
