    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for anyone looking for something reliable and well-cared for. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and still looks sharp parked in the driveway! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure right now. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2), featuring the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for a robust, linear power delivery across the rev range. This unit features the desirable 6-speed G96 manual transaxle, providing crisp gear engagement and precise heel-and-toe downshifts. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts that offer exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic upgrade, and the rear main seal (RMS) remains dry. Braking is handled by four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers over ventilated rotors, ensuring consistent thermal management under load. This driver-focused example is ready for the twisties, offering the visceral, analog experience synonymous with the Stuttgart marque.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
