    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a reliable, well-cared-for car that is ready for the road. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic paint that still holds a high-gloss shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free environment with well-preserved leather upholstery that shows only light bolstering wear on the driver's side. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium audio system and navigation, is fully functional. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health: the engine idles smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes were serviced last season. It has a complete service history, including a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need an upgrade anytime soon. This is a solid, honest car that performs beautifully.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
