    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a purist\u2019s specification featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing direct tactile feedback through the drivetrain. The VANOS system has been recently inspected, ensuring optimal variable valve timing, while the factory limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up under load. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining the platform's signature neutral handling. While the aesthetics show honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the powertrain and suspension geometry are dialed for immediate performance.",
